================================================================================
HWP / HWPX FORMAT NOTICE
================================================================================

HWP (Hangul Word Processor) is a document format historically associated with
Hancom Inc. HWPX is the OWPML XML-based open standard for the same format
family. This project does not bundle or distribute any Hancom-proprietary
binaries; all format handling is performed by @rhwp/core, an independent
open-source implementation.

Korean form / template files in any corpus/ subdirectory are referenced for
testing and are subject to the licensing terms of their original sources;
see corpus/SOURCES.md for provenance details.
